Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Char boldly infiltrated Jaburo,\Nthe Earth Federation Forces Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,However, with the heroic efforts\Nof Katz, Letz, and Kikka...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...and with the Gundam's fierce pursuit,\NChar had no choice but to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.78,0:01:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn Char...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:02:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A Decoy in Space
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.25,0:02:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tianem Fleet will be\Ndeparting Jaburo at 2100 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like your White Base to leave\Ntwo hours before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.18,0:02:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A full two hours ahead, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct. Oh, we'll be sending\Nthree other decoy ships as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having the Tianem Fleet\Nhead straight for Luna II...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...while the White Base takes the opposite\Nsatellite orbital course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll move in to attack\NZeon's space fortress, Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base will depart\Nat 1900 hours today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ensign Mirai, take good care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Once Solomon falls,\NZeon's resources will be so low...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...they will inevitably ask for peace\Nnegotiations, and the war will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll let me find you a husband then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That's right, you have a fiancé.\NForgive my rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be my fiancé, but\Nit was arranged by our parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that he fled to Side 6\Nto avoid the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to face it sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base will be departing in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Have all stations ready to go by then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Who's in charge of\Nthe White Base crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- What do you want with him?\N- Just tell me where he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright! You're wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant JG Sleggar Law.\NI've just been transferred here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mirai. Have we been notified?\N- Oh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My luck must be improving,\Nif I get to work with such a lovely lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings. I'm Mirai Yashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sayla Mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks to me like you're troubled\Nabout some other guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where do I bunk down?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The first step to this great battlei\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should the Federation Forcesrious...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...then our people will remember today{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We pray that you will fight well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a great big guy\Njust like Mr. Ryu was before he died!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's as nice as Ryu though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he's smart mouthed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, we'll be taking off soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands to your stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Release the docking locks!\NWhite Base, take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Airspace clear! Open hatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wow, look at all the birds!\N- Pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Look to portside if you have a minute.\NIt's a flock of flamingos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll record it on video.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you have my authorization.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's the Trojan Horse up to, Lt. Tokwan?\N- Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems they've left Jaburo\Nin South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be within combat range in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Was Lady Kycilia quite upset?\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought as much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If this Zanzibar hadn't been\Nstanding by to test the Bigro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...I couldn't have pursued\Nthe Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to see the Bigro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, show it to me.\NI need to come up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to high speed combat,\Nthis Bigro mobile armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...puts mobile suits to shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't build a battle plan\Naround one machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. But we've also got two Doms\Nand an untested mobile armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Doms? Aren't they for land combat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir! But these are Rick Doms\Nwith powered-up verniers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- They've been remodeled?\N- Yes. Much more effective than Zaku-types.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Speed it up!\NWe'll be heading out soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Assemble the pilots!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as we know where\Nthe Trojan Horse is headed, we'll attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship pursuing us looks like\Na Zanzibar-class warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, they'll catch up in 20 minutes\Nand we'll be under direct attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Stay on this course\Nand accelerate at Point E3.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:08:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That way it'll look like the White Base\Nis heading straight toward the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Char will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla, what are you still doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- There's barely time to check the G-Armor.\N- I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be sure that Char is coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... There's some fateful attraction\Nbetween him and the White Base. Right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you scared?\N- Who isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Mirai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's tired,\Nand that's why she's afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the Trojan Horse's projected course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're headed for the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For the moon?! Are they after\NLady Kycilia's Granada base?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- I doubt it.\N- Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trojan Horse is just a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's probably a different fleet\Ntaking off from Jaburo right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:09:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we have to change course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious? If we turn our backs\Non the Trojan Horse, they'll attack us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- We'll have to launch a preemptive strike!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Zanzibar located! Maximum magnification.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How many minutes until they attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, we'll be under attack\Nin 2 minutes, 20 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro and Sayla!\NPrepare to launch in the G-Sky and G-Bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the Guncannon ready on standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Open all gun turrets!\NOpen beam cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Tokwan, are you ready to launch the Bigro?\N- Sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick Doms, prepare to launch next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tokwan and two others, launching now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}G- Sky, G-Bull E-Z, take off at once!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deploy to the White Base's rearts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks to me like you're troubled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're doing this to take revenge\Non the Zabi family...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can't approve of that way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}G- Sky! Here I go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Bull E-Z, launching now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla, distance yourself a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If we took a direct hit right now,\Nthey could destroy both of us at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be careful now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go too fast,\Ngravity will make you plummet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember to fly as if you were ascending.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Rear missiles, intercept quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... just you watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you evade the speed of my Bigro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe how powerful it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's gripping me at a poor angle.\NI'll use my beam cannons...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what if my brother\Nis piloting this mobile armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, Ms. Sayla, you've got to ascend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Three enemy mobile suits confirmed.\NPlease send out the Guncannon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Have Kai launch the Guncannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Lieutenant Sleggar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah? What Is It? I'm right below the bridge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- What do you specialize in?\N- Artillery, fighter craft, take your pick!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you take care of\Nthe main cannons, Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- On one condition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the White Base toward the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in inertial flight,\Nso you should be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But then they'd catch up with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I won't do it.at I'd hit anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen well. Just attack for 15 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,if we fire any longer than that, we risk\Nshooting down our own mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't looking good...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- We'll get them with the guns at the back!\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Go get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trojan Horse has gotten better...\NI wonder if they have a new captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A civilian entering the military and\Njoining the Trojan Horse crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Artesia...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Artesia...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the last time I saw her,iform.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Artesia, who was intelligent,e.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way she'd board\Na space warship again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Halt your fire in three seconds!\NHit your mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. That wasn't on purpose at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lieutenant Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant. Let me remind you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...that you may be older than me\Nbut I still have command authority. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn about to starboard so that I can use\Nthe White Base's main cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't right now!\NWait a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The power isn't increasing... Why?!\NIt doesn't rev up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Rear missiles!\NFiring angle, plus 12 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! This is how you\Nput up a barrage of missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's maneuvered beneath me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about guts!\NIf you keep coming below me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...you could be pulled down. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the three enemy machines\Nis a mobile armor class weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hurry with the Guncannon's launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! What's taking you so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right! It's a long story, but I'm ready{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back up Amuro and Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger that! Here I go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Secure the Guntank to the launch exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use it as a gun turret! Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that! I'll inform Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the White Base about 180 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice going, Lieutenant Bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.49,0:15:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How about taking over at the main cannons?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Mirai, I'll leave the ship in your hands.\NI'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, where could they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't spend the rest of my life\Nbeing depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know how Ms. Sayla and Amuro\Ncan keep fighting like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A-At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got the upper hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use this opportunity\Nto transfer to Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I've got to lower its speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A direct hit and she's gone...\Nbut I've gotta stop her from plummeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? I'm starting docking procedures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Yes. But hurry up, Amuro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, what kind of person do you think\Nis piloting that mobile armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh? Why do you ask?\N- N-Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Amuro! A Dom is coming, so hurry!\N- Okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro!\N- It's okay! Don't worry, I'll take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Fighter! Docking now complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Altitude of mobile suit combat decreasing.\NWe can open fire on enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, prepare for fleet combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad we can't use our J-type missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll attack them as we evade their fire!\NAim carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Entering firing range in 30 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has the longer firing range...\Nus or the Trojan Horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose only God knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Artesia, I assume you're not on board...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Evade their fire every three seconds.\N- Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Entering firing range in 20 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We can fire in 20 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,15 seconds! All hands, prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:18:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how powerful\Nthe White Base's main cannons might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}3...2...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here it comes! Return fire!\N- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fire yet! Lure them in, and then fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire missiles continuously!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You persevered well! Now fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Zanzibar...\NI'll shoot you down somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Head for the Trojan Horse\Non a collision course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But sir...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be less likely to get hit than\Nif we weave about. I guarantee it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Zanzibar isn't evading fire!\NThey're on a collision course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're doing what?!\NMirai, evade! Starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:19:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the only one who would dare\Nto use these tactics!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as Sayla said! Char's come after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trojan Horse is losing its nerve!\NArtillery, take good aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like that?!\NThat's for trying to ram into my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire rear missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up... or running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd the other Dom go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The faster it is, the less accurate the shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you what a Bigro can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? I've picked up some baggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be the Gundam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, if it is... the pilot would have fainted\Nfrom the sudden acceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! Didn't the pilot pass out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the other mobile suits\Nand the Zanzibar?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,One of their mobile suits has retreated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They destroyed Tokwan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me go after them, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They're like a baby bird\Nthat's wandered into our yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- There'll be plenty more chances.\N- Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get started on repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla.\NWhy did you ask about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Back there, you asked who I thought\Nwas piloting the mobile armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that the enemy was so tough...\NThat's the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We can declare this first stage a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.15,0:22:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. I think we were\Nable to mislead the Zanzibar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Lieutenant Sleggar.\NYou were the only one with a direct hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just a fluke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more impressed by how you all did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.21,0:22:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's gotten faster, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- So how'd it go?\N- It was scary when we passed the Zanzibar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Those seemed like Char's tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.39,0:22:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Char, huh?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody else could've pulled that off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Man... I really do admire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla, you shot down a mobile suit!\NThat's quite something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.06,0:22:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on I just barely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.11,0:22:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play it down. I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.57,0:22:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an incredibly strong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.09,0:22:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm going to take a quick shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, but you've only got five minutes.\NThe Zeons'll be back in no time at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.20,0:22:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that! Wanna join me, Ms. Mirai?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.14,0:22:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to go on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.96,0:22:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sure.\N- Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're coming with you!\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.84,0:23:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,After shaking off Char's heated pursuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.62,0:23:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...the White Base is met by\Na Musai fleet, led by Lieutenant Dren.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleggar desperately fights them off...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the Gundam stages a fearless charge\Nagainst the Musais.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.27,0:23:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NBreakthrough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.26,0:23:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.59,0:23:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Breakthrough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
